      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALVARINO (1) made a nice return at his latest appearance a week ago, coming from the back row and finishing a head away in second at Tamworth. Fitter for that and should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position so has winning claims. TWO CRACKED CORN (3) has been racing well at this circuit and distance. Led from this draw and boxed on to be beaten 3.8m two back before a fourth from a wide barrier at her latest appearance. Should enjoy an economical run from this draw. Good enough to take out a race like this. D J ROCK NZ (8) draws wide but has been producing some decent efforts at Menangle including a placing two back. DOUBLE SAID (7) draws wide but ended last prep with a pair of placings and has been readied for his return with a trial win.",
